data.description: Curb appeal and more! This fabulous 3 bedroom 2 bath home with master suite on main floor has it all!  This home is ideally located just off Riverwatch Parkway and minutes from the Augusta National, the Augusta Medical District, as well as all the conveniences of both Columbia County and Richmond County.  You will love the beautiful wood floors that run throughout the main level and the open living room and formal dining area.  In the kitchen, you will enjoy a tiled backsplash, plenty of cabinets and counter space and room for a table or island.  The Owner's suite is located on the main level with a walk in closet plus a full bath with ceramic tile flooring and a beautiful tiled shower. Two, large additional bedrooms and full bathroom are located upstairs.  This home sits on a beautiful, secluded lot with a newly painted large deck that leads to a spacious backyard.  The tall crawl space offers more storage space and easy access.  This home is minutes to the Augusta Canal, walking and bike trails, restaurants, shopping, and more!  Come see this home today!
